subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: The project (AWP) seeks to harness the goodwill Liberia is currently experiencing through enhancing Government's capacity to transform this goodwill into concrete resource mobilization while also appropriately allocating the received funding for development priorities.
subproject.title: Aid Coordination
